h3%3E%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch6%20class%3D%22date%22%3EJune%2028%2C%202017%3C%2Fh6%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3E%3Ch6%3EThing%20to%20Do%3C%2Fh6%3E%3Ch3%3EFart%20in%20Front%20of%20Someone%20Sleeping%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch6%20class%3D%22date%22%3EJune%2017%2C%202017%3C%2Fh6%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3E%3Ch6%3EThing%20to%20Do%3C%2Fh6%3E%3Ch3%3EOverreacting%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20boss%20comes%20in%2C%20and%20you%20stand%20up%20tall%20and%20proud%2C%20and%20all%20he%20does%20is%20laugh%20at%20you.%20Suddenly%20veins%20pop%20out%20of%20your%20head%20and%20you%20push%20him%20out%20the%20window.%20However%20he%20survived%20and%20lived.%20Thats%20until%20the%20ambulance%20ran%20over%20him.%20Then%20he%20was%20truly%20dead%2C%20I%20mean%20wow.%20What%20a%20truly%20ironic%20thing%20to%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch6%20class%3D%22date%22%3EMay%201%2C%202017%3C%2Fh6%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3E%3Ch6%3EThing%20to%20Do%3C%2Fh6%3E%3Ch3%3EFart%20on%20Your%20Dog%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EHe%E2%80%99ll%20probably%20like%20it.%20Dogs%20are%20weird.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch6%20class%3D%22date%22%3EOctober%2026%2C%202016%3C%2Fh6%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3E%3Ch6%3EThing%20to%20Do%3C%2Fh6%3E%3Ch3%3ESticking%20Your%20Butt%20in%20the%20Air%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch6%20class%3D%22date%22%3ESeptember%2028%2C%202016%3C%2Fh6%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3E%3Ch6%3EThing%20to%20Do%3C%2Fh6%3E%3Ch3%3EDye%20Your%20Hamster%20in%20the%20Car%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EGet%20some%20pink%20dye%20and%20dump%20it%20all%20over%20your%20hamster%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch6%20class%3D%22date%22%3ESeptember%2017%2C%202016%3C%2Fh6%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3E%3Ch6%3EThing%20to%20Do%3C%2Fh6%3E%3Ch3%3ESmell%20a%20Mom%E2%80%99s%20Butt%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EMaybe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch6%20class%3D%22date%22%3EAugust%2010%2C%202016%3C%2Fh6%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3E%3Ch6%3EThing%20to%20Do%3C%2Fh6%3E%3Ch3%3ESleeping%20on%20a%20Chair%20in%20Front%20of%20Bird%20Poo%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBirds%20poop%2C%20you%20sleep%2C%20now%20there%20is%20poop%20on%20your%20seat!%20(This%20is%20supposed%20